channel.title: Anyone tried signing up for Yotube?
channel.description: Hey guys, im having and issue right now with youtube. Im trying to make a channel with my google account but whenever i click "My Channel" A box opens up asking me to click continue. When i do click it, it just says "Working..." and stays there for hours until i exit the web browser. I am using Safari on my mac, and iv also tried on Windows 7 on "Internet explorer, google chrome, and firefox" but they all still have the same problem.
